    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable

UserProfile
    name Text
    slug Text
    user UserId
    UniqueSlug slug
    UniqueProfile user

Book
    isbn Text
    title Text
    author Text
    UniqueIsbn isbn
    deriving Eq

Library
